  <p>Curious how the Liberal Party of Canada responded to the 2008 financial crisis (<a href="/?f%5Bdomain%5D%5B%5D=liberal.ca&q=recession&search_field=all_fields">a search for "recession" in 2008, liberal.ca</a>)? How the Canadian Centre for Policy Alternatives <a href="/?f%5Bdomain%5D%5B%5D=policyalternatives.ca&q=%22Michael+Ignatieff%22&search_field=all_fields">reacted to Michael Ignatieff</a>? Now you can check it all out.</p>
